title: Toadhalla Alpha Channel: Premium Access Pass
body:
Toadhalla is currently an alpha channel located in the Discord community - to have access, you must verify that you have a miceontoad v1/v2 nft. My proposal intends to add utility to the $stack LP pool by placing an additional percentage with royalties from secondary sales that goes to the pool for more stability.  As we know, stacked won’t circulate as much as miceontoadz due to the incentive to stake. However, miceontoadz would continue to circulate and increase in volume and popularity as Toadhalla is known to be the premium alpha channel with expansion and premiums being added soon.
....and they’re part of of the toad fam.
